```
        if (num_consumers > 16)
        {
            throw Exception("Number of consumers can not be bigger than 16", ErrorCodes::BAD_ARGUMENTS);
        }
```

As we enlarge the consumers we find the consume rate increase , so why this limit is setting to 16? On what kind of machine  we find this experience value?  If we had better machines can we enlarge it some how ?
Thanks
